Discussion:The linear motor actuator for $137.99 is a great choice for the design of a macamadamia nutcracker. It has a max force of 90kg, which allows the ratios between the applied force and the nut to be 2.7. 
However, this device is pretty useless considering that most people do not crack their own macamademia nuts, and this would end up being used once in 10 years and take up a lot of storage space in the kitchen. 
